overview:
FMS provide custom built Fleet Management and Training software solutions for vehicle and equipment fleets.

Our company prides itself on the vast amount of knowledge we hold in this sector.

FMS’ mission is to provide 100% functional and tailor-made software solutions that meet and exceed our customers’ expectations. As a result of continuous growth and development, we are now able to deliver customized solutions with a level of flexibility that truly sets us apart.

In a business field where customer needs are in a state of constant change, our flexible approach means we are ready to respond quickly, in the most appropriate and cost effective manner.
